{"tid":939593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港將來要靠80 90後","createTime":"2018-12-13T09:04:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T05:55:28.000Z","uid":26535,"like":23,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c195d5955a8a8c3710903c82941df373fa0f7435","tid":939593,"uid":26535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T09:04:06.000Z","msg":"啱啱經過上水某中學 xxxx<br />\n<br />\n4個學生妹 居然用超流利支那狗語溝通<br />\n<br />\n我就係到諗 香港下一代(00)後應該都支那化左<br />\n<br />\n話佢哋&rdquo;骨子裡&rdquo;係中國人都唔過份 因為真係支那人生(最少半隻)<br />\n<br />\n依家坐得局長位嘅 個個高薪厚職 即退休之後可以咬<br />\n長粮 實理撚得你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到80後 依家人生漸入高峰 你地依家為錢為將來<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">賣港刷共鞋 唔緊要</span></span>但<br />\n係 你地上左位之後 唔好忘記你地係 <span style=\"color: red;\">純香港人</span>呀！ 講真香港冇權冇勢 要改變真係好難 但係他朝一日 勿忘初衷 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">等依家班人退嚟之時 就係香港真正改變嘅時候</span></span>"},{"pid":"423f79b572292ecacbc0d3293b5cee3243a405a5","tid":939593,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T03:37:54.000Z","msg":"大家返工做到高層識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f953e1c0feb653a255e7fd131087f78cfdbfbde","tid":939593,"uid":89514,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T03:42:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ed4c2b5b8c431a1871d1c292e8339bd2bab1557","tid":939593,"uid":223256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T03:44:04.000Z","msg":"其實我有興趣<br />\n想知呢班只講師蝗語既00<br />\n後畢業後點搵野做<br />\n返大陸搵?<br />\n香港邊有工係只講蝗語?"},{"pid":"ac060738e68ef7580221ec951b0809df725a964c","tid":939593,"uid":89514,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T03:49:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bea3e47c3a74e4f57ea91f23f64204790e511923","tid":939593,"uid":56147,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2ed4c2b5b8c431a1871d1c292e8339bd2bab1557","tid":939593,"uid":223256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-